{"tid":122521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8年11警員吞槍自殺","createTime":"2017-02-16T05:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T02:21:51.000Z","uid":9348,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e08dddbdc8c5906214cd1ae7b43972fae13281a","tid":122521,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"8年11警員吞槍自殺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20161209/photo/1209-00176-051b1.jpg?t=1487223772911\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161209%2Fphoto%2F1209-00176-051b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1487223772911&h=6c21fc26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】最近八年共有十一宗警務人員吞槍自殺，其中九人死亡。昨日自尋短見的警長，疑個人情緒出現問題，包括喪親之痛難平復。精神科專科醫生丁錫全稱，一個人<del>如失去至親或身邊重要的人，除了感到哀傷外，或會感內疚及自責，這些情緒未必能隨時間沖淡，如一直未有處理，哀傷會一路延續，「爆煲」時情況或一發不可收拾，尤其是在一些特別日子如死忌、生日或其他節日等</del>賭輸錢欠債還唔起，都會令其更添愁緒，更可能做出極端行為如自殺等，建議當事人不要有顧忌，應盡早尋求協助。<br />\n<br />\n丁指，這些負面情緒的形成與職業無關，即使是警察或其他一些形象上硬朗及堅強的職業，均無可避免會受情緒困擾，而警察更是其中一個較高危職業，因部分警員隨身帶備佩槍，變相容易取得用作尋死的工具，一旦有尋死衝動，就會較容易實現到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69bbed9444abf04abe5e623e775bfe6704bf0e5","tid":122521,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"會有幾多個正評"},{"pid":"27a2d2eb6b82ad43561639c5c16822af3f7302ee","tid":122521,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110918/photo/0918-00174-001b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20110918%2Fphoto%2F0918-00174-001b5.jpg&h=48f6e3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20110918/photo/0918-00407-004b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2F